tooltipElement.title: Help for feature: Display Name
tooltipElement.text: If set, the optional display name is shown for the project throughout the Jenkins web GUI. As it is for display purposes only, the display name is not required to be unique amongst projects. If the display name is not set, the Jenkins web GUI will default to showing the project name.
